{"tid":855634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到呢句時候 仲要幫保皇狗轉移視線","createTime":"2018-10-10T07:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T07:26:22.000Z","uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d605025ac82c899dbcbfa8b8b1db19c61e309329","tid":855634,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:22:51.000Z","msg":"我都唔講乜野<br />\n如果你地仲覺得佢冇可疑<br />\n你地就係自己鳩自己攞來<br />\n我就一直屌保皇狗反保皇狗<br />\n佢呢？<br />\n呢個時候都仲要用泛民幫保皇狗轉移視線<br />\n沙中線特權調查保皇狗反對<br />\n佢唔出post屌保皇狗<br />\n記者被拒發簽証<br />\n佢唔出post屌保皇狗<br />\n施政報告發表不滿大叫<br />\n佢反而出post<br />\n我估就算泛民平靜聽完<br />\n佢一樣出post話佢地乜都唔做架啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/151906_f4fb9d8b0edb8e4ab5078d1c4da49e01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F151906_f4fb9d8b0edb8e4ab5078d1c4da49e01.png&h=77b7a2e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ab8cd4b8ebdb3280e27beeea70ff6b73d086d1a","tid":855634,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:26:22.000Z","msg":"一個雨革完就即番大陸做四年野<br />\n做完即刻番香港加入學聯<br />\n你都仲信<br />\n抵你地死"}]}